# cert client authn
<Location /{{app_url_base}}/ws/>
RequestHeader set Content-type application/xml
SSLRequireSSL
SSLVerifyClient require
SSLVerifyDepth 5
SSLOptions +StdEnvVars +ExportCertData
Options -MultiViews
order allow,deny
allow from all
</Location>



